                        <p>Spine: 'David Kimchi. Sepher Ham-Mikhlol. Joseph Ben Chaiyim. Ba'al Kenaphayim. Hebrew. Brit. Mus. Oriental Ms. 1022.'</p>
                     
                     
                     
                     </binding>
                  
                  
                  
